caption.title: Observed versus predicted presence/absence of any yellow fever reported event between 1984 and 2013.
caption.p: A: Presence (red) or absence (white) of YF report between 1984 and 2013, B: GLM prediction for probability of report for the FOI model; C: GLM prediction for probability of report for the R0 model. GLM: Generalized Linear Model. Maps were produced from GADM version 2.0.
